snippet.title: 3D Challenge Showcase: A Found 3DS Tech Demo!
snippet.description:
An unreleased 3DS tech demo from Nintendo has recently been found and dumped, so let's take a look at it as well as some interesting tidbits hidden within!

Release Post:
➤ https://twitter.com/forestillusion/status/1319640664758382593

3D Gameplay:
➤ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WjEG-Hriqx0

Soundtrack Rip:
➤ https://mega.nz/file/kHYmGLLR#tvbVrNNuxufr1JWPyBQ-TTwDhOSNSjHc2hEi2JaSeoE

00:00 Introduction & Background
02:24 3D Challenge Demo
04:42 Unused Content
08:48 Epilogue
-----------------------------------------------------
A big thank you to my subscribers and Patreon patrons for your support!
If you like what you see, consider subscribing or even clicking the bell to be notified of new videos. :)
